(2411, 40, 'wpcf-experience_field', 'Since 1998, after having worked for a number of smaller patent firms in Israel, Ms. Bleiberg has over 20 years experience in drafting and prosecution of patent applications, specializing in the fields of medical devices and mechanics. Currently with the firm of Ehrlich &amp; Fenster for seven years, serving clients in Israel as well as worldwide, including the leading Universities and Academic Institutions in Israel and many well-known major companies.'),
