(20, 2, '2013-05-22 11:14:14', '2013-05-22 11:14:14', 'So as to ensure that your e-mail communications are received by the respective persons, in particular e-mail communications containing instructions having a deadline, and so as to ensure the deadlines are timely met, please always verify our confirmation of receipt of your instructions in a timely fashion. It is preferable to also send us a confirmation copy of your instructions simultaneous by fax.\r\n\r\nYou can also contact us via the form below:\r\n[gravityform id="2" name="Please fill in the form Below"]', 'Career Opportunity at Ehrlich & Fenster', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jobs', '', '', '2014-01-15 11:32:27', '2014-01-15 11:32:27', '', 0, 'http://ipatent.com/?page_id=20', 0, 'page', '', 2),
