ty Rights: Patent preparation and prosecution, Opinions regarding Product Clearance, Infringement/Non-Infringement, Patentability and Validity searches.', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '14-revision-11', '', '', '2013-07-07 10:48:18', '2013-07-07 10:48:18', '', 14, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=464', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
