(587, 2, '2013-08-20 14:13:55', '2013-08-20 14:13:55', 'Nowadays, industrial design and the aesthetic features of products are becoming increasingly more important to both companies and consumer. A Design protects the overall visual appearance of a product or a part of a product, resulting from its features- contours, colors, shape, texture or materials. Meaning, legal protection is given to the way the product looks. A Registered Design can be a valuable intellectual property right, as it may create the basis of an infringement action.\r\n\r\nOur Design Department, specializes in identifying the needs of each and every client, especially those whose products are seasonal in nature and require expedited processing. Our design department also specializes in preparing and filing Design application in Israel and abroad, as well as in design patents prosecution and enforcement. In filing design applications, as in all other aspects, we ensure achievement of our clients business goals in the procurement of strong IP portfolio and combined strategy.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Design', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '539-revision-3', '', '', '2013-08-20 14:13:55', '2013-08-20 14:13:55', '', 539, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=587', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(588, 2, '2013-08-19 07:12:59', '2013-08-19 07:12:59', 'The Litigation Support department deals with cases which involve actual or potential litigation or which involve due diligence or analysis of patents or patent portfolios during acquisition or investment.\r\n\r\nWe advise clients on preparing for litigation and help clients to find suitable representation overseas. We continue to be involved in the technical and interface aspects of these litigations remaining deeply involved in these cases during their entire lifetime. We have had a major part in cases of this type in the US, the EPO, the UK, Germany, Japan, China and Singapore. We also represent clients in discussions with foreign patent holders who assert their patents against our clients.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Litigation Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '541-revision-2', '', '', '2013-08-19 07:12:59', '2013-08-19 07:12:59', '', 541, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=588', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(589, 2, '2013-07-28 08:26:25', '2013-07-28 08:26:25', 'The firm helps clients identify, determine, and broaden the protection scope of their core Intellectual Property. This is achieved by analyzing and assessing the potential business opportunities that may emerge from the client’s innovative technologies and areas of invention. Ehrlich &amp; Fenster strategic advantage is in its ability to identify the individual or multi-core technologies often hidden within a technological development. The firm pursues all the potential business directions available to a client including buying, in-and-out licensing, selling and international expansion.\r\n\r\nEach department is involved in drafting and prosecuting patent applications, including opposition procedures, in rendering opinions regarding IP matters, IP related Due Diligence processes, and in devising IP and commercialization strategies. There are over a dozen patent attorneys having Ph.D. degrees in all disciplines, with most Department heads having a doctorate degree.\r\n\r\nEhrlich &amp; Fenster provides patent prosecution services in a broad range of technologies to many small and mid-sized companies, as well as to large clients that have critical timing requirements, complex patent applications likely to be embroiled in litigation or interferences, or require specialized technical needs.\r\n<h3>Among our practice areas:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;">Biotech, Immunology, Agrotechnology, Bioinformatics, Biochemistry</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;">Pharmacology, Chemistry</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;">Physics, Mechanics, Medical Devices, Cleantech</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;">Electronics, Elecrooptics, Computer Hardware</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 1.714285714; font-size: 1rem;">Computer Software, Telecommunications, Business Methods</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Patents', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '523-revision-2', '', '', '2013-07-28 08:26:25', '2013-07-28 08:26:25', '', 523, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=589', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
