(756, 2, '2013-09-11 13:38:13', '2013-09-11 13:38:13', 'A trademark is a valuable IP right, as it is a valuable marketing tool. A trademark distinguish one’s goods and services from those of the competitors, as it allows customers to differentiate between products or services.\r\n\r\nOur trademark department specializes in identifying and selecting strong, protectable trademarks. Our trademark practice also consists of in-depth trademark availability and infringement analyses, advising clients on practical ways to enhance protection of their IP rights, searching and clearing proposed trademarks, obtaining local and foreign trademark registrations, complex prosecution of 3D trademarks and slogans, seizure of counterfeit products at the Customs, domain name registrations and disputes, including trademark oppositions, rival proceedings and cancellation actions before the Israeli Trademark Office.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Trademarks', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '35-revision-7', '', '', '2013-09-11 13:38:13', '2013-09-11 13:38:13', '', 35, 'http://ipatent.co.il/?p=756', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
